---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navigation from '../components/Navigation.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | PT. Indo Energy Tekniko" description="Privacy Policy for PT. Indo Energy Tekniko website.">
	<Navigation />
	<main class="pt-32 pb-24">
		<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
			<h1 class="font-heading text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-navy-900 mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
			<p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mb-10">Last updated: May 18, 2026</p>

			<div class="space-y-8 text-slate-600 text-base leading-relaxed">
				<section>
					<h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-3">1. Information We Collect</h2>
					<p>When you submit an inquiry through our contact form, we collect the following information:</p>
					<ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1">
						<li>Full name</li>
						<li>Company name</li>
						<li>Email address</li>
						<li>Phone number (optional)</li>
						<li>Service and industry of interest</li>
						<li>Project description</li>
					</ul>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-3">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
					<p>We use the information you provide solely for the purpose of:</p>
					<ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1">
						<li>Responding to your engineering project inquiries</li>
						<li>Providing proposals and quotations</li>
						<li>Communicating about our services</li>
						<li>Improving our website and services</li>
					</ul>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-3">3. Data Sharing</h2>
					<p>We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your personal information to third parties. Your data is kept strictly confidential and is only accessed by authorized personnel within PT. Indo Energy Tekniko.</p>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-3">4. Data Security</h2>
					<p>We implement appropriate security measures to protect your personal information against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction.</p>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-3">5. Cookies</h2>
					<p>This website may use essential cookies to ensure proper functionality. We do not use tracking or advertising cookies.</p>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-3">6. Your Rights</h2>
					<p>You have the right to:</p>
					<ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1">
						<li>Request access to the personal data we hold about you</li>
						<li>Request correction or deletion of your data</li>
						<li>Withdraw consent for data processing</li>
					</ul>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-3">7. Contact</h2>
					<p>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:</p>
					<p class="mt-2 font-medium text-navy-900">sales@indoenergytekniko.com</p>
				</section>
			</div>
		</div>
	</main>
	<Footer />
</Layout>
